# Network Fundamentals

## What is Networking

Network means when devices are connected together. Internet is a giant network in which there is many other networks (private and public). The World Wide Web (www) is used as a repository for storing and sharing information. To communicate and maintain order, devices must be both identifying and identifiable on a network.
1. What is the key term for devices that are connected together? Netwrok
2. Who invented the World Wide Web? Tim Berners-Lee
